it is funny how stupid people actually are.  just cause you don't detect a virus/trojan doesn't mean there isn't one.  any home made trojan can easily pass detection from scanners, and any existing mass used trojan can be easily modified to be hidden from scanners.  just like some people say keygens don't have trojans but that is such a lie, many have them.  it is the perfect lie, because legit keygens do come up as virus or trojan so sticking one in a keygen can easily get past peoples scanners since they think it is safe anyways.  

don't be fooled, you aren't always getting these files for 'free', 99% of these programs are trial programs, that you can easily download from the main site.  you're better off finding a serial and downloading direct from the main site.
